!iflang [english]

!begin_node Cookie, SMAL

(!B)Small (!nolink [AES]) icon fonts(!b)

Holds in the lower-value WORD the height of the (!nolink [AES]) icon font (SMALL) 
in pixels (as used by vst_height). The higher-value WORD optionally 
holds the height of the IBM font. Is to be set by every program that 
alters the size of the SMALL font (e.g AESFONT by H. Schmidt). More 
detailed definition in RUBY (M. Nick).

!end_node

